{"tid":1467913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非同勇武唇齒相依 萬大事不分化不割","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:17:53.000Z","uid":219,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f331cad183ce39102aa9fa2c5d5ff70ef8cabfda","tid":1467913,"uid":219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"大家一齊諗下聽日之後既對策 停止互相指罵"},{"pid":"0ce62e39ed6060e33a03cbe36cf3b5dea8bc4dab","tid":1467913,"uid":294412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:43:10.000Z","msg":"付xx的私人資料我唔方便再係度貼圖了<br />\n<br />\n我聽到巴打講佢係環時記者，真係得啖笑。<br />\n環時俾左卡片佢姐，佢唔會變環時既人<br />\n我未100％ FC 以下搵到既資料。<br />\n機場手足，果個好大機會係堅記者 仲同香港01有微妙關係<br />\n<br />\n從手足係佢個袋搵到既信件顯示<br />\n公司名為：世華萬向資訊（北京）有限公司<br />\n註明為台港新聞部編輯<br />\n我自己都係上網查，搵到個地址：北京经济技术开发区地盛西路1号数码庄园<br />\n繼續google 個地址喇，有趣的事情出現了！<br />\n搵到間叫中國數碼的公司<br />\n中國數碼的地址 與 世華萬向一樣<br />\n香港地址：香港新界荃湾沙咀道6号嘉达环球中心12楼<br />\n北京地址：北京经济技术开发区地盛西路1号数码庄园<br />\n<br />\n更得意既係，香港01 亦位於嘉達環球中心。<br />\n而在中國數碼的董事會裡面，其中一個就係于品海<br />\n眾所尻知，于品海就係香港01 創辦人<br />\n<br />\n中國數碼地址 ＝ 世華萬向地址<br />\n香港01創辦人 ＝ 中國數碼董事<br />\n<br />\n根據暫時搵到的資料，果個人係記者的機會率就大好多了<br />\n雖然佢可能係做唔見得光既野<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可以一齊搵資料，我夠鐘返工喇！<br />\n<br />\nBe Water!"},{"pid":"fba527c6dbd5f1c8b48bd9970521844abbfa457a","tid":1467913,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:43:42.000Z","msg":"搞大818 <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/KviyEOR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKviyEOR.gif&h=d2c73fea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f04bfa0bbf4dedaa861804c70785ebc8d06b8d79","tid":1467913,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:11.000Z","msg":"【訓撚醒未呀】港共政府 無辦法係機場清場 但 可以 連登分化粉碎呢個活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467822</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc708099e6f2694af0d9804da10d798974e5f815","tid":1467913,"uid":219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:10.000Z","msg":"鬼係有 <br />\n但最大既敵人都係我地自己內部分裂"},{"pid":"2e8f472abedfc7b12fa2577bb4376ad18573f48e","tid":1467913,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:33.000Z","msg":"何妖實恥笑<br />\n我由頭到尾無割過 無被割 無被指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班撚樣 少少野都割又分化互屌互指責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---------<br />\n記住 反對/屌人時 比埋建議 咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾句建議姐818 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各自爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多手足受傷 被捕 點解我地仲企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因 為 未 完 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">818見</span>"},{"pid":"8f060221562a38a07b7887ac83c93d91b17c8951","tid":1467913,"uid":219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:49.000Z","msg":"停止內鬥 一致對外"},{"pid":"d407a1567131c844e6a39dfe0a00fc5e2df8f9c0","tid":1467913,"uid":260088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:26.000Z","msg":"［置頂］［緊急］ 民間記者會請幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466254</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">民間記者會